                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-7-off32 t17861213-7-crimeloc34"></join>; on the 30th of October I lost a sheet off the prisoner's bed; she was my <rs id="t17861213-7-deflabel35" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-7-defend72 t17861213-7-deflabel35"></join>; my wife missed it, and told me; I asked the prisoner for it; she said, she did not know any thing about it; I took her up, and the constable found the sheet wrapped round her body.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17861213-7-person76">
                  THOMAS
                   NICHOLLS
               <interp inst="t17861213-7-person76" type="surname" value="NICHOLLS"></interp>
