                     <interp inst="t17861213-7-person76" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>On the 30th of October I found the sheet about her; it was pinned round the same as a petticoat.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I told my mistress I had washed my under petticoat, and I pinned the sheet round me to keep me warm; I was afraid to tell my mistress that I had took the liberty to take it.</p>
